title: League Of Legends Log In Screen Not Opening ( Launch button doesn't open it)
body: Since the Legacy skins are coming, I thought I'd try my hardest to fix my LoL (been broken for 2 weeks). I've tried practically everything and nothing works. I tried repairing, but it doesnt do anything. When I force a re-patch the EULA pops up twice and I don't recieve the terms and conditions. I'm currently hoping the repatch magically works, but any suggestions on how to fix this would be nice. Thanks!
